Parents should instil moral values in youth and advise young women to stop dating older men to prevent spread of HIV, Kitui Governor Julius Malombe&rsquo;s wife has said. &ldquo;We have to restore our traditional values of decency and decorum. We must guide girls against greed that draws them to sponsors who infect them with the deadly HIV,&rdquo; Edith Mawia said on Thursday.&ldquo;Girls should not engage with sponsors to get things they do not have.